President Obama released a statement on Ms Ride's death: 'As the first American woman to travel into space, Sally was a national hero and a powerful role model. 

'She inspired generations of young girls to reach for the stars and later fought tirelessly to help them get there by advocating for a greater focus on science and math in our schools.

She will be missed, but her star will always shine brightly. 

